{"id":17995,"date":"2022-12-31T04:23:31","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:23:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-dung-xe-hybrid.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:23:31","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:23:31","slug":"toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-dung-xe-hybrid","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-dung-xe-hybrid\/","title":{"rendered":"Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0a ra 5 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe hybrid"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe Toyota hybrid \u00edt kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong, h\u00e3ng Nh\u1eadt khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng l\u01b0u \u00fd 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">B\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t pin<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe Toyota hybrid trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3i b\u1ee5i, b\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u1eafc quy c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb b\u1ea9n, t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn, gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t \u1eafc quy v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea7u ra.  ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.  Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1, xe s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a xe hybrid Toyota.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su.jpg\" title=\"toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a xe hybrid Toyota.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">N\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1, HV Inverter c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7t trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.  Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n theo d\u00f5i m\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, m\u1ee9c \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eefa v\u1ea1ch Th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea7y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1ef1 \u00fd m\u1edf n\u1eafp k\u00e9t n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t, ho\u1eb7c n\u00fat x\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1t trong khoang m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb b\u1ecfng. Chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u00e1p su\u1ea5t cao khi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.\u201d  , \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng ty cho bi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">12V .  pin<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u1eaec quy 12V l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn t\u00edch tr\u1eef, cung c\u1ea5p n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n tr\u00ean xe Toyota hybrid.  Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p pin y\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_310_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su.jpg\" title=\"1672435084_310_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_310_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_310_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_310_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd thay th\u1ebf vi\u00ean pin n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t.  T\u1ef1 \u00fd thay \u1eafc quy kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn xe, ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nguy c\u01a1 ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5, m\u1ea5t an to\u00e0n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">kh\u00f3a c\u1ea7n s\u1ed1<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng xe Toyota hybrid n\u00ean c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng phanh v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 P khi \u0111\u1ed7 xe.  \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n, m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid tr\u00ean xe.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb m\u1ee9c P khi xe ch\u01b0a kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_424_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su.jpg\" title=\"1672435084_424_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_424_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_424_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672435084_424_toyota-viet-nam-dua-ra-5-luu-y-khi-su.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb m\u1ee9c P khi xe ch\u01b0a kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng b\u00f4i tr\u01a1n h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean m\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng, ki\u1ec3m tra \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe.  Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 r\u00f2 r\u1ec9, hao d\u1ea7u b\u00f4i tr\u01a1n\u2026 n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a xe \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Tu\u1ea5n V\u0169<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">\u1ea2nh: TMV<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o